content:
  id: SRD-001
  kind: SRD
  title: System Requirements for the To-Do Example
  status: accepted
  scope: app
  owner: Engineering
  date: 2026-03-03
  canonicalKey: todo-app-srd
  tags[3]: frontend,architecture,spec
  dependsOn[1]: PRD-001
  supersedes[0]:
  supersededBy[0]:
  conflictsWith[0]:
  sections[7]{title,body}:
    Architecture Overview,Single-page React app with TypeScript and Vite with state in localStorage for zero backend setup.
    State Model,Each task stores id title notes priority completed dueDate tags and createdAt.
    Data Flow,React component state drives UI and persistence writes every mutation directly to localStorage.
    Filtering Model,Filters include all active completed overdue and high priority plus text search.
    Documentation Flow,All planning and design docs are authored in .toon files under docs and generated outputs are written to generated.
    Tooling,Node 22 React 18 Vite 5 TypeScript 5 plus the local agent-docs CLI package.
    Limitations,No authentication no multi-user sync and no backend API. This keeps setup light and focused on documentation workflow.
